6
00:01:23,625 --> 00:01:24,667
I was...

7
00:01:26,795 --> 00:01:29,547
in love with Ms. Choi.

8
00:01:50,777 --> 00:01:52,278
- You're here.
- Yeah.

9
00:01:55,448 --> 00:01:57,491
Why is it so dark in here?

10
00:01:57,492 --> 00:01:59,284
- Here.
- Thank you.

11
00:01:59,285 --> 00:02:01,996
The more alone you are,
the brighter your space should be.

12
00:02:02,705 --> 00:02:04,957
I made too much <i>geotjeori.</i>

13
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:07,544
You don't like it fermented.
Put it in your fridge.

14
00:02:08,711 --> 00:02:10,922
