18
00:02:26,771 --> 00:02:27,772
So it wouldn't leak.

19
00:02:28,731 --> 00:02:29,566
It won't.

20
00:02:40,034 --> 00:02:41,619
Would you like a cup of tea?

21
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,878
Sir.

22
00:03:00,972 --> 00:03:03,099
If an action carries emotion...

23
00:03:06,895 --> 00:03:08,521
that's when it becomes violence.

24
00:03:10,064 --> 00:03:11,732
Don't make me tell you

25
