51
00:04:42,365 --> 00:04:44,950
Having a meal with your boss
feels like work.

52
00:04:44,951 --> 00:04:45,994
Oh yeah?

53
00:04:47,203 --> 00:04:48,287
Just talking to myself.

54
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:51,541
Jesus, is it still talking to yourself
