97
00:06:48,408 --> 00:06:49,867
Those damn punks.

98
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:51,911
Damn it. Move!

99
00:06:55,998 --> 00:06:56,833
That was crazy!

100
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,341
Those bastards.

101
