125
00:09:00,206 --> 00:09:01,665
Is he still fucking behind us?

126
00:09:01,666 --> 00:09:03,292
Shit, what do we do?

127
00:09:05,586 --> 00:09:07,338
- What the hell?
- Those little...

128
00:09:09,173 --> 00:09:10,424
Step on it!

129
00:09:18,474 --> 00:09:20,810
This is crazy! Your driving is sick!

130
00:09:24,939 --> 00:09:28,609
