- She said she was hungry.

131
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:37,076
Hey, it's splashing me!

132
00:09:40,121 --> 00:09:40,955
Hey!

133
00:09:41,581 --> 00:09:43,456
- Hey! Pull over!
- Careful.

134
00:09:43,457 --> 00:09:45,041
