We were going this way.

153
00:10:49,857 --> 00:10:51,441
Inspector Im Han-rim was...

154
00:10:51,442 --> 00:10:54,653
- Hey, there. Wake up. Are you okay?
- Inspector Im was...

155
00:10:54,654 --> 00:10:58,323
She threw a bike under the car

156
00:10:58,324 --> 00:11:00,158
and stopped it.

157
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,242
Are you all right?

158
00:11:01,243 --> 00:11:03,120
She stopped them from fleeing.

159
00:11:05,915 --> 00:11:07,083
Pull yourself together.

160
00:11:08,459 --> 00:11:10,001
Yun-jin's just drunk.

161
00:11:10,002 --> 00:11:11,503
She had three bottles.

162
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:13,213
- She drank loads.
- She had more.

163
00:11:13,214 --> 00:11:14,131
She had a lot.

164
00:11:15,424 --> 00:11:18,385
They think we were trying to do
something to her.

165
00:11:18,386 --> 00:11:20,011
We're really all friends.

166
00:11:20,012 --> 00:11:21,472
- That's right.
- Totally.

167
00:11:24,266 --> 00:11:25,601
Are you really friends?

168
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,229
Yes, we are.

169
00:11:29,188 --> 00:11:31,189
So just leave us alone.

170
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:32,607
See? I told you.

171
00:11:32,608 --> 00:11:34,859
She said we're friends.
We're total besties.

172
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:36,194
- Exactly.
- Be quiet, punk!

173
00:11:36,195 --> 00:11:38,363
You've committed car theft,
unlicensed driving,

174
00:11:38,364 --> 00:11:39,698
