175
00:11:39,699 --> 00:11:42,117
- I'm sorry, sir.
- I'm sorry, sir.

176
00:11:42,118 --> 00:11:45,704
But the engine was running,
and we just got in out of curiosity.

177
00:11:45,705 --> 00:11:47,539
That's right. It's our hormones.

178
00:11:47,540 --> 00:11:49,874
We're impulsive.
It's what happens at our age.

179
00:11:49,875 --> 00:11:50,959
- It's our age.
- Yeah.

180
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:55,005
We're juvenile offenders for a reason.
We're really sorry.

181
00:11:55,506 --> 00:11:56,631
We're sorry.

182
00:11:56,632 --> 00:11:58,258
- We're sorry!
- We're sorry!

183
00:11:58,259 --> 00:12:01,094
