- We're sorry!

184
00:12:01,095 --> 00:12:02,847
Im Han-rim, don't.

185
00:12:04,265 --> 00:12:06,641
They know they won't be punished.

186
00:12:06,642 --> 00:12:07,767
That's correct.

187
00:12:07,768 --> 00:12:10,186
