188
00:12:10,187 --> 00:12:13,940
They know the police can't touch them,
as long as they play stupid,

189
00:12:13,941 --> 00:12:15,775
because they're underage.

190
00:12:15,776 --> 00:12:17,611
They know the law too well. Sit still.

191
00:12:18,738 --> 00:12:22,449
- Did you call the parents?
- Yes, but they'll be a while.

192
00:12:22,450 --> 00:12:24,618
Our homeroom teacher said
he'd come right away.

193
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:27,037
- Hand them over when he arrives.
- Okay.

194
00:12:27,538 --> 00:12:28,873
- Chief.
- Yes?

195
00:12:30,583 --> 00:12:32,041
What happens now?

196
00:12:32,042 --> 00:12:35,670
Serious cases go to juvenile court
and protective dispositions issued.

197
00:12:35,671 --> 00:12:38,466
But for a case like this,
we let them off with a warning.

198
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:42,887
I heard there's nothing
the school can do either.

199
00:12:45,014 --> 00:12:45,848
Here he comes.

200
00:12:46,432 --> 00:12:48,976
- You can hear from him directly.
- Hello, Mr. Lee.

201
00:12:51,479 --> 00:12:53,564
CUSTODY HANDOVER CONFIRMATION FORM

202
00:13:05,034 --> 00:13:06,451
We'll be on our way now.

203
00:13:06,452 --> 00:13:09,788
Come and see me first thing tomorrow.
We'll talk more then.

204
00:13:09,789 --> 00:13:10,705
- Okay.
- Thank you.

205
00:13:10,706 --> 00:13:11,706
We appreciate you.

206
00:13:11,707 --> 00:13:12,833
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

207
00:13:15,628 --> 00:13:16,711
- Goodbye.
- Thank you.

208
00:13:16,712 --> 00:13:17,712
Get her home safe.

209
00:13:17,713 --> 00:13:19,006
- Goodbye, sir.
- Take care.

210
00:13:23,177 --> 00:13:24,303
It's unsettling, right?

211
00:13:24,887 --> 00:13:27,055
Even I can't get used to
the way they speak.

212
00:13:27,056 --> 00:13:29,057
I hear you're from the ERPB?

213
00:13:29,058 --> 00:13:29,975
Yes.

214
00:13:30,476 --> 00:13:31,727
I'm Inspector Na Hwa-jin.

215
00:13:33,395 --> 00:13:34,396
Excuse me.

216
00:13:35,523 --> 00:13:38,775
