through the app these days, so...

221
00:13:47,576 --> 00:13:48,536
Damn it.

222
00:13:50,538 --> 00:13:53,832
I'm sorry.
I should have taught them better.

223
00:13:53,833 --> 00:13:56,251
Not at all. It's not for you to apologize.

224
00:13:56,252 --> 00:13:58,504
