226
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:05,553
They know all too well
that adults can't do anything to them.

227
00:14:07,847 --> 00:14:09,639
What about the school rules?

228
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:13,101
They say they're juvenile offenders.
Do you think rules will work on them?

229
00:14:13,102 --> 00:14:14,769
It'll be hard to expel them too

230
00:14:14,770 --> 00:14:17,898
because middle school education
is mandatory.

231
00:14:20,901 --> 00:14:21,735
Sir?

232
00:14:25,072 --> 00:14:26,448
<i>Juvenile offenders played you?</i>

233
00:14:27,366 --> 00:14:28,242
Yes, sir.

234
00:14:29,034 --> 00:14:32,453
I did hear that "juvenile offender"
is like a title from the heavens.

235
00:14:32,454 --> 00:14:35,249
I guess former special forces
are no match for them either.

236
00:14:36,292 --> 00:14:38,502
I want to too!

237
00:14:41,755 --> 00:14:42,590
Who are they?

238
00:14:43,883 --> 00:14:46,343
It's them. The invincible 14-year-olds.

239
00:14:47,011 --> 00:14:48,095
Bye.

240
00:14:49,972 --> 00:14:50,890
Shit.

241
00:14:54,435 --> 00:14:56,477
Bye!

242
00:14:56,478 --> 00:14:58,605
This is fun. Yes, fun indeed.

243
00:14:58,606 --> 00:15:00,982
- Did you say Hyeonjin Middle School?
- Yes, sir.

244
00:15:00,983 --> 00:15:02,735
