- Damn it.

253
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,843
Oh, hello.

254
00:15:28,844 --> 00:15:29,762
Hello.

255
00:15:30,512 --> 00:15:31,388
What's your name?

256
00:15:32,222 --> 00:15:33,222
Jung Seung-jin.

257
00:15:33,223 --> 00:15:35,184
Okay, Seung-jin. Get to class.

258
00:15:37,227 --> 00:15:39,063
See you later. Put my bag on my desk.

259
