262
00:15:46,153 --> 00:15:47,612
The ERPB is different.

263
00:15:47,613 --> 00:15:49,113
They're really here.

264
00:15:49,114 --> 00:15:51,199
You gave us a real gift yesterday.

265
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,785
I'm here to return the favor.
Give and take.

266
00:15:53,786 --> 00:15:55,119
What's give and cake?

267
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,914
We need to carry out
a proper investigation starting now.

268
00:15:57,915 --> 00:15:58,831
Are you free?

269
00:15:58,832 --> 00:15:59,874
- No.
- No.

270
00:15:59,875 --> 00:16:01,084
Why? Are you busy?

271
00:16:01,085 --> 00:16:03,087
No, we're free. It's fine, right?

272
00:16:03,587 --> 00:16:05,755
Okay, get to the counseling room.

273
00:16:05,756 --> 00:16:06,965
To the counseling room.

274
00:16:06,966 --> 00:16:08,676
Nice. We get to skip class.

275
00:16:10,844 --> 00:16:12,428
The ERPB came for us. We made it.

276
00:16:12,429 --> 00:16:14,597
- I'll be famous.
- I don't have a signature.

277
00:16:14,598 --> 00:16:15,848
- I need one.
- This is mad.

278
00:16:15,849 --> 00:16:16,767
What's this?

279
00:16:18,018 --> 00:16:19,560
I told you I'll investigate.

280
00:16:19,561 --> 00:16:22,188
I know.
This is a bluff to buy time, right?

281
00:16:22,189 --> 00:16:23,523
- Busted!
- Busted, right?

282
00:16:23,524 --> 00:16:25,024
They say they'll investigate.

283
00:16:25,025 --> 00:16:28,778
But they're isolating us and are probably
taking the victims' statements.

284
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:31,531
Well, aren't you Detective Conan?

285
00:16:31,532 --> 00:16:33,116
Then let's confess now.

286
00:16:33,117 --> 00:16:35,452
Go ahead. Do whatever the hell you want.

287
00:16:42,793 --> 00:16:44,377
No one will find out

288
00:16:44,378 --> 00:16:46,255
what is said here.

289
00:16:47,047 --> 00:16:50,551
If Min Ji-ung's crew has ever bullied you
or you've seen them bully others...

290
00:16:52,052 --> 00:16:53,262
No such thing happened.

291
00:16:54,513 --> 00:16:55,513
No.

292
00:16:55,514 --> 00:16:56,764
We're not that close.

293
00:16:56,765 --> 00:16:59,642
I honestly don't know anything,
so please stop asking me.

294
00:16:59,643 --> 00:17:01,936
I'm not sure.

295
00:17:01,937 --> 00:17:03,397
No, nothing like that.

296
00:17:12,990 --> 00:17:13,949
Well...

297
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:17,452
Apparently, the student
you asked me to investigate

298
00:17:17,453 --> 00:17:20,998
does hang around Min Ji-ung,

299
00:17:21,498 --> 00:17:24,043
but they're not exactly friends.

300
00:17:24,626 --> 00:17:25,752
What are they, then?

301
00:17:25,753 --> 00:17:28,255
She wouldn't tell me
anything more than that.

302
00:17:30,132 --> 00:17:32,133
And where is Yun-jin?

303
00:17:32,134 --> 00:17:34,470
She's here today,
but she wasn't at her desk.

304
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:40,726
- Where is this?
- The recycling area behind this building.

305
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:43,686
I don't think this is it.
Let's look elsewhere.

306
00:17:43,687 --> 00:17:46,731
The sly jerks move in packs
and make their hideouts

307
00:17:46,732 --> 00:17:49,525
