They're easier to handle than teachers.

309
00:17:56,825 --> 00:18:00,120
Given those variables
and conditional value...

310
00:18:01,789 --> 00:18:03,748
- What about here?
- Where is this?

311
00:18:03,749 --> 00:18:06,418
There's a standalone building
right beside this gym.

312
00:18:16,345 --> 00:18:18,013
I think this is the place.

313
00:18:18,847 --> 00:18:19,848
Look at this.

314
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,646
Come this way. This way!

315
00:18:36,657 --> 00:18:38,783
