357
00:21:27,953 --> 00:21:29,620
Man, you're pissing me off.

358
00:21:29,621 --> 00:21:31,289
TTEOKBOKKI
MALATANG LEVEL 2

359
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:32,958
CHEWY COOKIES
DUBAI CHOCOLATE

360
00:21:38,046 --> 00:21:40,673
Aren't you having lunch?
Can't you afford it?

361
00:21:40,674 --> 00:21:42,926
No, I'm just trying to lose weight.

362
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:44,803
You'd be pretty if you did.

363
00:21:45,387 --> 00:21:46,345
Do you think so too?

364
00:21:46,346 --> 00:21:49,308
