They can't be bad.

371
00:22:05,741 --> 00:22:07,950
Take one,
and you'll feel the fucking difference.

372
00:22:07,951 --> 00:22:10,162
Look, it's a heart.

373
00:22:10,996 --> 00:22:12,122
Aren't they cute?

374
00:22:14,958 --> 00:22:15,792
Watch this.

375
00:22:17,627 --> 00:22:18,837
Put it in here.

376
00:22:25,010 --> 00:22:26,636
Just treat me if you lose weight.

377
00:22:31,391 --> 00:22:33,226
- Don't drink it, then.
- I will.

378
00:22:40,734 --> 00:22:43,945
TYPICAL DANCE SKILLS
OF A MIDDLE SCHOOL GIRL

379
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:48,283
Yun-jin.

380
00:22:49,576 --> 00:22:51,619
You look damn pretty in your Shorts video.

381
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:53,330
Is it because you've lost weight?

382
00:22:53,914 --> 00:22:54,789
Do I look it?

383
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:56,875
The pills are working wonders.
Want another?

384
00:22:59,669 --> 00:23:00,629
Do you have more?

385
00:23:01,296 --> 00:23:02,381
Of course.

386
00:23:05,175 --> 00:23:06,009
Heart.

387
00:23:07,969 --> 00:23:10,554
Is there any chance
