409
00:24:32,804 --> 00:24:34,347
Shit! I could just...

410
00:24:36,766 --> 00:24:37,601
Oh Yun-jin!

411
00:24:38,185 --> 00:24:41,438
I trust that you won't disappoint us.
Hand over the money.

412
00:24:43,106 --> 00:24:43,940
Gosh.

413
00:24:48,403 --> 00:24:49,404
Nice.

414
00:24:53,533 --> 00:24:54,367
Up it 20,000.

415
00:24:55,327 --> 00:24:56,161
20,000 won?

416
00:24:58,413 --> 00:24:59,414
What if no one buys?

417
00:25:00,457 --> 00:25:02,292
You've got a goldfish brain?

418
00:25:03,043 --> 00:25:06,129
You bought it
even after the price went up, so raise it.

419
00:25:07,547 --> 00:25:08,423
Say something.

420
00:25:10,759 --> 00:25:12,093
Well...

421
00:25:13,428 --> 00:25:15,096
Could I stop doing this now?

422
00:25:16,181 --> 00:25:18,350
It's been really tough for me,
and I'm scared.

423
00:25:20,101 --> 00:25:21,645
Fuck! Damn it!

424
00:25:24,564 --> 00:25:25,689
Give me the pills.

425
00:25:25,690 --> 00:25:27,734
- What?
- Give it here.

426
00:25:28,318 --> 00:25:31,738
I guess you don't need
the pills either, do you?

427
00:25:37,827 --> 00:25:39,119
Holy shit.

428
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:40,997
That's 50,000 won gone.

429
00:25:46,002 --> 00:25:46,836
