Seriously, what the hell?

434
00:25:58,807 --> 00:25:59,933
Do it properly, damn it.

435
00:26:01,434 --> 00:26:02,561
Do better, all right?

436
00:26:56,072 --> 00:26:58,575
SCHOOL POLICE REPORTING BOX

437
00:27:05,999 --> 00:27:07,291
Hey, so long!

438
00:27:07,292 --> 00:27:09,418
- Be gone!
- Bye-bye!

439
00:27:09,419 --> 00:27:12,087
- Sorry.
- Watch it. The police are here.

440
00:27:12,088 --> 00:27:13,131
Wow.

441
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:15,299
They're going.

442
00:27:15,300 --> 00:27:17,301
It's all over for Min Ji-ung now.

443
00:27:17,302 --> 00:27:19,720
