446
00:27:22,724 --> 00:27:26,018
- I hope they're expelled.
- But really, who reported them?

447
00:27:26,019 --> 00:27:28,563
I don't know who it was, but thanks.

448
00:27:30,482 --> 00:27:32,941
HYEONJIN MIDDLE SCHOOL

449
00:27:32,942 --> 00:27:36,612
Heat transfers from hotter objects
to cooler objects.

450
00:27:36,613 --> 00:27:38,155
This happens in three ways.

451
00:27:38,156 --> 00:27:40,616
Let's start with conduction.

452
00:27:40,617 --> 00:27:43,911
We often grill a lot of pork belly
for meals, don't we?

453
00:27:43,912 --> 00:27:46,789
When the meat touches the hot grill,

454
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:50,876
the particles in contact start moving fast

455
00:27:50,877 --> 00:27:53,588
and pass energy
to other particles in turn.

456
00:27:54,464 --> 00:27:55,882
Hello, sir.

457
00:27:57,801 --> 00:27:58,760
Hurry to your seat.

458
00:28:01,471 --> 00:28:03,223
We'll carry on with the lesson.

459
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:08,645
You fucking bitch.
You actually snitched to the cops?

460
00:28:10,063 --> 00:28:11,314
That's right, Yun-jin.

461
00:28:12,399 --> 00:28:13,566
They got your letter.

462
00:28:14,150 --> 00:28:16,485
We were investigated thanks to you.

463
00:28:16,486 --> 00:28:19,280
But then, we were let go with a warning.

464
00:28:21,116 --> 00:28:23,117
She must have thought we'd go to prison.

465
00:28:23,118 --> 00:28:24,618
Yeah, as if.

466
00:28:24,619 --> 00:28:25,954
Too bad.

467
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:30,125
We're juvenile offenders,
so we won't be sent to prison.

468
00:28:36,214 --> 00:28:37,090
Get in there.

469
00:28:39,843 --> 00:28:41,052
Get some rest.

470
00:28:45,724 --> 00:28:48,058
Ji-ung!

471
00:28:48,059 --> 00:28:51,020
Please open the door, Ji-ung.

472
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:52,731
Ji-ung.

473
00:28:53,231 --> 00:28:54,774
I'm sorry.

474
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,735
Please open the door.

475
00:28:57,652 --> 00:28:58,485
Ji-ung.

476
00:28:58,486 --> 00:29:00,238
If you did something wrong...

477
00:29:02,699 --> 00:29:04,284
you should be punished.

478
00:29:05,744 --> 00:29:06,870
Isn't that right?

479
00:29:07,370 --> 00:29:09,497
Let's take a picture
to remember this moment.

480
00:29:14,753 --> 00:29:17,422
- I'm hungry. Let's go get some food.
- We can't hear you.

481
00:29:18,089 --> 00:29:19,882
- What do you want to eat?
- Pork cutlet.

482
00:29:19,883 --> 00:29:21,342
- Pork cutlet?
- That's crazy.

483
00:29:42,113 --> 00:29:44,699
<i>Can you testify
to everything you just said?</i>

484
00:29:50,413 --> 00:29:52,498
- So we can punish--
- Don't do that.

485
00:29:52,499 --> 00:29:54,334
Is the ERPB any different?

486
00:29:54,834 --> 00:29:58,879
Our homeroom teacher, the school,
and even the police couldn't do anything.

487
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,715
Ji-ung always came looking for me.

488
00:30:02,217 --> 00:30:05,637
Every time I thought
it would be enough or he would stop,

489
00:30:06,137 --> 00:30:08,348
he always came back.

490
00:30:10,517 --> 00:30:12,393
I'm always the only one who gets hurt.

491
00:30:13,728 --> 00:30:16,481
This will only end once I die.

492
00:30:34,374 --> 00:30:36,000
The ERPB is different.

493
00:30:37,585 --> 00:30:41,297
The ERPB is serious
about students who have been hurt.

494
00:30:43,049 --> 00:30:44,342
So trust us.

495
00:30:46,636 --> 00:30:47,971
I will protect you.

496
00:30:58,648 --> 00:30:59,607
Sir.

497
00:31:04,863 --> 00:31:06,113
WRITTEN STATEMENT
GO FUCK YOURSELF

498
00:31:06,114 --> 00:31:09,658
You're gaining points nicely.

499
00:31:09,659 --> 00:31:10,785
Thank you, sir.

500
00:31:19,377 --> 00:31:21,837
It's more than just beating and bullying.

501
00:31:21,838 --> 00:31:23,047
It's drug trafficking.

502
00:31:23,923 --> 00:31:25,215
Those kids I told you about

503
00:31:25,216 --> 00:31:28,469
