523
00:32:41,584 --> 00:32:43,126
- Annoying, right?
- Fucked, right?

524
00:32:43,127 --> 00:32:45,546
- It's fucked, right?
- It's dog shit, right?

525
00:32:52,637 --> 00:32:54,222
Fuck, don't come near me.

526
00:32:54,931 --> 00:32:55,890
Daddy!

527
00:33:02,271 --> 00:33:03,480
Welcome.

528
00:33:03,481 --> 00:33:05,315
Come here. Good job.

