795
00:49:53,657 --> 00:49:56,576
- Stand against the wall.
- Face forward. Raise your arms.

796
00:49:57,160 --> 00:49:58,411
- Hands on head.
- Eyes ahead.

797
00:49:58,412 --> 00:50:00,080
Stand against the wall.

798
00:50:00,580 --> 00:50:01,664
What are you doing?

799
00:50:01,665 --> 00:50:03,000
Hands on your head.

800
00:50:13,719 --> 00:50:14,928
Out of the way!

801
00:50:20,392 --> 00:50:23,019
I'm already here
serving the maximum possible sentence,

802
00:50:23,020 --> 00:50:25,104
so killing you won't change a thing.

803
00:50:25,105 --> 00:50:26,565
Inmate 1397, get off him!

804
00:50:29,067 --> 00:50:30,693
Get inside!

805
00:50:30,694 --> 00:50:32,737
From now on, this place is hell,

806
00:50:32,738 --> 00:50:34,321
and I'll make sure to find you.

807
00:50:34,322 --> 00:50:36,866
Let's play hide and seek all day long.

808
00:50:36,867 --> 00:50:38,076
Stay still!

809
00:50:38,618 --> 00:50:40,495
There are lots like me here.

810
00:50:42,998 --> 00:50:44,999
Right, guys?

811
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:47,043
Right? Aren't I right?

812
00:50:47,044 --> 00:50:48,253
Right?

813
00:51:05,896 --> 00:51:07,396
MINISTRY OF EDUCATION

814
00:51:07,397 --> 00:51:09,190
The worst human rights violators!

815
00:51:09,191 --> 00:51:11,150
The ERPB must apologize!

816
00:51:11,151 --> 00:51:13,360
Apologize!

817
00:51:13,361 --> 00:51:15,029
The worst human rights violators!

818
00:51:15,030 --> 00:51:16,072
Hey, he's here!

819
00:51:16,073 --> 00:51:18,158
Minister!

820
00:51:19,159 --> 00:51:21,286
Just a moment, Minister!

821
00:51:21,912 --> 00:51:25,122
Minister!

822
00:51:25,123 --> 00:51:27,124
- Minister.
- Just stop for a moment!

823
00:51:27,125 --> 00:51:29,044
- Minister!
- Hey!

824
00:51:29,544 --> 00:51:30,837
I said stop!

825
00:51:31,338 --> 00:51:32,296
Hold on, Minister!

826
00:51:32,297 --> 00:51:33,422
- Minister!
- Sir!

827
00:51:33,423 --> 00:51:35,382
- Wait a moment!
- Sir!

828
00:51:35,383 --> 00:51:37,134
- Minister!
- Get out of the way!

829
00:51:37,135 --> 00:51:38,052
Just a moment.

830
00:51:38,053 --> 00:51:39,470
Minister, just a moment.

831
00:51:39,471 --> 00:51:42,432
Is it true
that you sent our children to prison?

832
00:51:43,350 --> 00:51:44,767
Yes, that's right.

833
00:51:44,768 --> 00:51:47,353
How could you send
those young children to prison?

834
00:51:47,354 --> 00:51:49,397
It's a field trip.

835
00:51:49,981 --> 00:51:51,482
They'll end up there eventually.

836
00:51:51,483 --> 00:51:52,483
- What?
- Ridiculous.

837
00:51:52,484 --> 00:51:54,151
- Are you kidding me?
- What nonsense.

838
00:51:54,152 --> 00:51:57,113
How could you?
You didn't even get our permission!

839
00:51:57,114 --> 00:51:59,698
Would you have allowed it if we had asked?

840
00:51:59,699 --> 00:52:01,701
- What?
- You should've at least let us know!

841
00:52:02,285 --> 00:52:04,121
I seriously can't believe this guy.

842
00:52:04,704 --> 00:52:06,247
This is driving me nuts.

843
00:52:06,248 --> 00:52:07,833
Great detail there.

844
00:52:08,708 --> 00:52:10,126
Why didn't you write in detail

845
00:52:10,127 --> 00:52:12,628
what your kids did
and where they were taken

846
00:52:12,629 --> 00:52:14,255
on those protest signs?

847
00:52:14,256 --> 00:52:15,422
- Excuse me?
- Seriously?

848
00:52:15,423 --> 00:52:16,674
I can't believe this.

849
00:52:16,675 --> 00:52:19,385
Goodness, where do you get the nerve?

850
00:52:19,386 --> 00:52:20,636
Excuse me, mister.

851
00:52:20,637 --> 00:52:24,473
I'll do whatever it takes to drag you down
from there, so be ready for it.

852
00:52:24,474 --> 00:52:27,935
Being a minister isn't all that
in this day and age.

853
00:52:27,936 --> 00:52:29,770
Forget it. Don't bother.

854
00:52:29,771 --> 00:52:33,274
Ji-ung's mom, let's go to the press
and bring this to the National Assembly.

855
00:52:33,275 --> 00:52:34,733
- That's perfect.
- Sounds great.

856
00:52:34,734 --> 00:52:35,901
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

857
00:52:35,902 --> 00:52:38,571
No need for that.
Come to the children's school tomorrow.

858
00:52:38,572 --> 00:52:41,532
Why? Do we have to come
just because you tell us to?

859
00:52:41,533 --> 00:52:44,244
It will be the last chance
to see your children.

860
00:52:44,744 --> 00:52:45,995
So do as you please.

861
00:52:45,996 --> 00:52:47,538
- What did you say?
- What?

862
00:52:47,539 --> 00:52:49,623
- What do you mean?
- What last chance?

863
00:52:49,624 --> 00:52:51,417
- What last chance?
- Wait, come back!

864
00:52:51,418 --> 00:52:52,419
Minister!

865
00:53:12,230 --> 00:53:13,314
Go inside.

866
00:53:13,315 --> 00:53:14,816
- Mom.
- It's Dad. Dad!

867
00:53:15,400 --> 00:53:16,776
- Dad!
- Ji-ung.

868
00:53:19,321 --> 00:53:20,446
Yes, darling.

869
00:53:20,447 --> 00:53:22,240
My goodness, darling.

870
00:53:28,955 --> 00:53:31,373
I'm so upset.
What on earth are you wearing?

871
00:53:31,374 --> 00:53:32,500
Are you crazy?

872
00:53:33,251 --> 00:53:34,669
Excuse me.

873
00:53:35,295 --> 00:53:37,922
Why are our children in this state?

874
00:53:37,923 --> 00:53:41,217
I looked into it a bit,
and you did all sorts of nonsense.

875
00:53:41,218 --> 00:53:43,510
You got them to do the dishes?
Even I don't!

876
00:53:43,511 --> 00:53:47,223
Also, I heard you put them
in the same space as murderers!

877
00:53:47,224 --> 00:53:49,225
As a human, how could you do that?

878
00:53:49,226 --> 00:53:54,104
How could you send children
as young as 14 years old to prison?

879
00:53:54,105 --> 00:53:55,982
Don't you know they're underage?

880
00:53:57,108 --> 00:53:58,109
Now.

881
00:54:00,195 --> 00:54:02,072
Do you know what this is?

882
00:54:02,822 --> 00:54:04,115
What is it?

883
00:54:06,243 --> 00:54:07,410
Tell them. What is it?

884
00:54:10,497 --> 00:54:13,540
They're just diet pills.

885
00:54:13,541 --> 00:54:16,293
The kids asked me
to get them for them, so I did.

886
00:54:16,294 --> 00:54:17,587
What's the problem?

887
00:54:26,638 --> 00:54:27,472
Oh my God.

888
00:54:28,056 --> 00:54:29,807
What are you doing? You must be crazy.

889
00:54:29,808 --> 00:54:31,309
Oh my goodness!

890
00:54:32,227 --> 00:54:34,395
What's the matter?

891
00:54:34,396 --> 00:54:35,813
I swallowed it.

892
00:54:35,814 --> 00:54:37,439
For God's sake.

893
00:54:37,440 --> 00:54:38,858
- Mom! What do I do?
- Oh my!

894
00:54:39,484 --> 00:54:41,860
Why? What's wrong? What?

895
00:54:41,861 --> 00:54:44,572
You said they're diet pills.
Don't you want to lose weight?

896
00:54:45,156 --> 00:54:46,324
What's wrong? Jesus!

897
00:54:48,576 --> 00:54:49,994
Mom, what do I do?

898
00:54:49,995 --> 00:54:52,204
- Mom!
- They're just supplements.

899
00:54:52,205 --> 00:54:53,456
That's enough.

900
00:54:55,625 --> 00:54:56,668
They're supplements?

901
00:54:57,252 --> 00:54:59,211
Shit, I'm fucked.

902
00:54:59,212 --> 00:55:01,338
You seem aware
these pills shouldn't be taken.

903
00:55:01,339 --> 00:55:04,091
- Mom, I nearly got fucked.
- Why? What's wrong?

904
00:55:04,092 --> 00:55:06,844
These pills,
the same shape as the ones he just took,

905
00:55:06,845 --> 00:55:09,431
are designer drugs containing phentermine.

906
00:55:11,599 --> 00:55:13,852
They were feeding them to their friends.

907
00:55:16,771 --> 00:55:19,148
Mom, I really didn't know.

908
00:55:19,149 --> 00:55:20,692
I didn't know what I was doing.

909
00:55:21,276 --> 00:55:22,109
Mom.

910
00:55:22,110 --> 00:55:23,445
He says he didn't know!

911
00:55:24,362 --> 00:55:26,363
They're juvenile offenders for a reason.

912
00:55:26,364 --> 00:55:30,993
Children have no idea
what consequences these things can have.

913
00:55:30,994 --> 00:55:35,664
That's why adults should protect
juvenile offenders.

914
00:55:35,665 --> 00:55:38,417
- Isn't that right? Aren't I right?
- What do kids know?

915
00:55:38,418 --> 00:55:39,878
- They're young.
- Deputy Bong.

916
00:55:41,004 --> 00:55:42,380
Please look here.

917
00:55:42,922 --> 00:55:47,385
This is evidence that they distributed
and sold these drugs to their friends.

918
00:55:48,470 --> 00:55:51,598
They have made
over 50 million won this way.

919
00:55:52,140 --> 00:55:53,140
It's huge, isn't it?

920
00:55:53,141 --> 00:55:54,309
MIN JI-UNG
56,131,893 WON

921
00:55:55,727 --> 00:55:58,605
Juvenile offenders
who should be protected?

922
00:55:59,356 --> 00:56:00,564
Sure.

923
00:56:00,565 --> 00:56:01,899
EVIDENCE OF ASSAULT BY MIN JI-UNG

924
00:56:01,900 --> 00:56:03,485
Then what about the victims here?

925
00:56:05,570 --> 00:56:06,696
Who will protect them?

926
00:56:08,782 --> 00:56:10,909
But they didn't know.

927
00:56:11,409 --> 00:56:14,912
It's not too late to teach them now.
Isn't that right, sir?

928
00:56:14,913 --> 00:56:17,456
- Let's pool money for the settlement.
- Yes, let's.

929
00:56:17,457 --> 00:56:19,501
We'll use it to compensate the victims.

930
00:56:20,001 --> 00:56:23,380
Then we just need to get the petitions
and submit them, don't we?

931
00:56:23,880 --> 00:56:24,880
That's right.

932
00:56:24,881 --> 00:56:26,465
We'll do everything necessary.

933
00:56:26,466 --> 00:56:29,134
- So please go easy on them, sir.
- Just this once...

934
00:56:29,135 --> 00:56:32,471
They're still young children
with their whole lives ahead of them.

935
00:56:32,472 --> 00:56:35,057
Shouldn't they be given a chance, sir?

936
00:56:35,058 --> 00:56:36,351
Shut up!

937
00:56:39,771 --> 00:56:42,023
"You must not harm others."

938
00:56:43,274 --> 00:56:45,402
"You must not hurt others."

939
00:56:47,570 --> 00:56:50,198
These are the things
you should have taught them.

940
00:56:52,575 --> 00:56:54,411
If you couldn't, the school should have.

941
00:56:56,329 --> 00:56:59,791
If the school couldn't,
society should have taught them.

942
00:57:01,418 --> 00:57:03,753
But everyone failed,
so the ERPB had to step in.

943
00:57:04,254 --> 00:57:06,297
At least the ERPB will teach them.

944
00:57:07,507 --> 00:57:09,884
When a person does wrong,
they will be punished!

945
00:57:10,385 --> 00:57:13,680
Perpetrators should never stand taller
than their victims!

946
00:57:19,769 --> 00:57:21,771
That's how they must take responsibility.

947
00:57:33,158 --> 00:57:34,993
Mom, do something.

948
00:57:35,785 --> 00:57:37,036
- Mom?
- Just a moment.

949
00:57:37,871 --> 00:57:41,582
He says he is truly repentant, sir.
I mean, Minister.

950
00:57:41,583 --> 00:57:42,542
I'm sorry.

951
00:57:43,126 --> 00:57:44,960
You won't ever do that again, will you?

952
00:57:44,961 --> 00:57:45,878
- No.
- No.

953
00:57:45,879 --> 00:57:47,880
I'm sorry! I'm really sorry!

954
00:57:47,881 --> 00:57:51,425
I won't ever do it again.
I have truly repented, sir.

955
00:57:51,426 --> 00:57:53,051
Please let me off this once.

956
00:57:53,052 --> 00:57:54,803
Please give me another chance.

957
00:57:54,804 --> 00:57:56,514
Please, I beg you.

958
00:57:57,098 --> 00:57:58,057
I really...

959
00:57:58,558 --> 00:58:01,268
- Please.
- Right, you should've repented like this.

960
00:58:01,269 --> 00:58:04,105
I really can't go back. I can't.

961
00:58:04,606 --> 00:58:06,691
But we're not the ones

962
00:58:08,276 --> 00:58:09,277
to forgive you.

963
00:58:52,987 --> 00:58:53,905
You guys...

964
00:58:56,866 --> 00:58:58,743
I will never forgive you.

965
00:59:02,539 --> 00:59:05,708
I never had a single day of peace,
all because of you.

966
00:59:07,293 --> 00:59:10,755
I was so terrified
that I couldn't even breathe.

967
00:59:12,507 --> 00:59:13,675
To me,

968
00:59:15,593 --> 00:59:16,761
school was hell.

969
00:59:19,931 --> 00:59:22,975
From now on, this place is hell,
and I'll make sure to find you.

970
00:59:22,976 --> 00:59:25,979
<i>Let's play hide and seek all day long.</i>

971
00:59:27,855 --> 00:59:30,567
Why should I run away
when you're the ones who did wrong?

972
00:59:31,484 --> 00:59:33,278
I want to go to school too!

973
00:59:33,778 --> 00:59:35,779
I want to graduate too!

974
00:59:35,780 --> 00:59:37,740
What the hell is she saying?

975
00:59:38,658 --> 00:59:39,909
I'm a juvenile offender.

976
00:59:40,618 --> 00:59:43,203
It means I'm allowed to kill you,
fucking bitch!

977
00:59:43,204 --> 00:59:45,206
Ji-ung! Oh my God!

978
00:59:52,964 --> 00:59:56,467
The parents' request
for the release of the children

979
00:59:57,760 --> 00:59:59,511
is hereby denied.

980
00:59:59,512 --> 01:00:00,721
No, wait...

981
01:00:00,722 --> 01:00:02,723
- Hereby denied?
- What do you mean, denied?

982
01:00:02,724 --> 01:00:03,974
What do you mean?

983
01:00:03,975 --> 01:00:07,060
The children will be taken back
to the juvenile prison.

984
01:00:07,061 --> 01:00:08,729
- No.
- What do you mean? No.

985
01:00:08,730 --> 01:00:09,896
- Mister!
- Dad!

986
01:00:09,897 --> 01:00:11,274
No!

987
01:00:14,902 --> 01:00:15,945
Mom! What do I do?

988
01:00:17,155 --> 01:00:18,405
Mom!

989
01:00:18,406 --> 01:00:19,991
Oh no, my baby!

990
01:00:21,451 --> 01:00:22,285
Ji-ung!

991
01:00:25,997 --> 01:00:28,291
My baby! Move aside for a second!

992
01:01:13,878 --> 01:01:15,755
Thank you.

993
01:01:17,423 --> 01:01:21,844
<i>From now on, the ERPB
will educate juvenile offenders.</i>

994
01:01:22,637 --> 01:01:26,599
Seventy years have passed,
yet there has only been empty talk.

995
01:01:27,266 --> 01:01:30,394
The juvenile system hasn't changed,
but crimes have increased.

996
01:01:30,395 --> 01:01:33,980
As a result, innocent students
are still suffering today.

997
01:01:33,981 --> 01:01:37,819
Since someone has to make changes,
the ERPB will step up.

998
01:01:38,820 --> 01:01:40,780
The law may exempt juvenile offenders,

999
01:01:41,280 --> 01:01:44,409
but the education system will not.

1000
01:01:47,954 --> 01:01:50,415
Hey, babe!

1001
01:02:07,348 --> 01:02:08,558
Fuck.

1002
01:02:13,312 --> 01:02:14,147
Get inside.

1003
01:02:16,274 --> 01:02:18,317
If you did wrong, you should be punished.

1004
01:02:32,623 --> 01:02:33,708
I'm sorry.

1005
01:02:56,814 --> 01:02:57,648
Get inside.

1006
01:03:01,527 --> 01:03:03,696
Feel the victims' pain.

1007
01:03:04,280 --> 01:03:06,073
You'll learn a lot in there.

1008
01:03:14,999 --> 01:03:15,958
Get inside.

1009
01:03:16,626 --> 01:03:17,585
Get inside.

1010
01:03:21,798 --> 01:03:23,758
How long do we have to stay here?

1011
01:03:24,509 --> 01:03:25,802
Until you're of age.

1012
01:03:26,844 --> 01:03:28,178
After that,

1013
01:03:28,179 --> 01:03:30,598
the law will hold you accountable anyway.

1014
01:03:38,940 --> 01:03:41,149
Yun-jin, I'm sorry.

1015
01:03:41,150 --> 01:03:42,901
Yun-jin!

1016
01:03:42,902 --> 01:03:44,569
I'm sorry. I'll never do it again.

1017
01:03:44,570 --> 01:03:46,697
Please open the door, Yun-jin.

1018
01:03:47,824 --> 01:03:48,866
Yun-jin.

1019
01:03:59,335 --> 01:04:00,168
Good work, guys.

1020
01:04:00,169 --> 01:04:01,962
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

1021
01:04:01,963 --> 01:04:03,089
Thank you.

1022
01:04:09,762 --> 01:04:11,721
Are you sure this is enough?

1023
01:04:11,722 --> 01:04:13,015
Yes, sir.

1024
01:04:15,017 --> 01:04:16,435
I really missed this.

1025
01:04:17,478 --> 01:04:18,312
All right.

1026
01:04:20,356 --> 01:04:21,524
Thanks for helping me.

1027
01:04:22,108 --> 01:04:24,819
Not at all.
I offered to help in the first place.

1028
01:04:26,737 --> 01:04:27,905
But in return,

1029
01:04:28,781 --> 01:04:30,408
please promise me one thing.

1030
01:04:33,119 --> 01:04:35,371
Please make sure
no one ends up like me again.

1031
01:04:37,540 --> 01:04:39,750
I think the ERPB
will be able to manage that.

1032
01:04:46,090 --> 01:04:47,675
Can I really drink this?

1033
01:05:01,731 --> 01:05:02,982
Hey, juvenile offender.

1034
01:05:06,193 --> 01:05:07,028
Yes?

1035
01:05:07,695 --> 01:05:09,280
You know the BS gang boss, right?

1036
01:05:11,490 --> 01:05:13,158
But I didn't mention that thing.

1037
01:05:13,159 --> 01:05:15,036
- Not a single word.
- Well done.

1038
01:05:15,828 --> 01:05:18,288
But our boss tends to be quite cautious.

1039
01:05:18,289 --> 01:05:20,333
- Do you know what I mean?
- Yes.

1040
01:05:22,043 --> 01:05:23,127
Goodbye.

1041
01:07:01,142 --> 01:07:04,103
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim
